{"id":"api/core/Pipe","title":"Pipe","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/Pipe\", \"name\": \"Pipe\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L850-L851\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L850-L851\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"pipe\">Pipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#pipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">本裝飾器用於將類標記為管道並提供配置元資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Decorator that marks a class as pipe and supplies configuration metadata.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/Pipe#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  \n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>選項</th><th>說明</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#name\">\n          <code>name</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td><p translation-result=\"on\">在範本中繫結時使用的管道名。\n通常使用 <a href=\"guide/glossary#case-types\">lowerCamelCase</a> 拼寫方式，因為名字中不允許包含減號（-）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The pipe name to use in template bindings.\nTypically uses <a href=\"guide/glossary#case-types\">lowerCamelCase</a>\nbecause the name cannot contain hyphens.</p>\n\n</td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#pure\">\n          <code>pure?</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td><p translation-result=\"on\">為 <code>true</code> 時，該管道是純管道，也就是說 <code>transform()</code> 方法只有在其輸入引數變化時才會被呼叫。管道預設都是純管道。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When true, the pipe is pure, meaning that the\n<code>transform()</code> method is invoked only when its input arguments\nchange. Pipes are pure by default.</p>\n\n</td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/styleguide#02-09\">樣式指南：管道名稱</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/styleguide#02-09\">Style Guide: Pipe Names</a></p>\n\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">管道類必須實現 <code><a href=\"api/core/PipeTransform\" class=\"code-anchor\">PipeTransform</a></code> 介面。比如，如果其名稱為 “myPipe”，則使用範本繫結表示式，比如：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A pipe class must implement the <code><a href=\"api/core/PipeTransform\" class=\"code-anchor\">PipeTransform</a></code> interface.\nFor example, if the name is \"myPipe\", use a template binding expression\nsuch as the following:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n{{ exp | myPipe }}\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">此表示式的結果會傳給管道的 <code>transform()</code> 方法。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">管道必須屬於某個 NgModule，才能用於範本。要使其成為 NgModule 的成員，請把它加入 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code> 元資料的 <code>declarations</code> 中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The result of the expression is passed to the pipe's <code>transform()</code> method.</p>\n\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">A pipe must belong to an NgModule in order for it to be available\nto a template. To make it a member of an NgModule,\nlist it in the <code>declarations</code> field of the <code><a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code> metadata.</p>\n\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">選項<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <a id=\"name\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>\n          <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n            <h3 id=\"name\">name<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#name\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n            <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L817-L825\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L817-L825\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n          </div>\n        </th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">在範本中繫結時使用的管道名。\n通常使用 <a href=\"guide/glossary#case-types\">lowerCamelCase</a> 拼寫方式，因為名字中不允許包含減號（-）。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The pipe name to use in template bindings.\nTypically uses <a href=\"guide/glossary#case-types\">lowerCamelCase</a>\nbecause the name cannot contain hyphens.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n            name: string\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n  <a id=\"pure\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>\n          <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n            <h3 id=\"pure\">pure<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Pipe#pure\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n            <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L826-L842\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L826-L842\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n          </div>\n        </th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">為 <code>true</code> 時，該管道是純管道，也就是說 <code>transform()</code> 方法只有在其輸入引數變化時才會被呼叫。管道預設都是純管道。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When true, the pipe is pure, meaning that the\n<code>transform()</code> method is invoked only when its input arguments\nchange. Pipes are pure by default.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n            pure?: boolean\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">如果該管道具有內部狀態（也就是說，其結果會依賴內部狀態，而不僅僅依賴引數），就要把 <code>pure</code> 設定為 <code>false</code>。\n這種情況下，該管道會在每個變更檢測週期中都被呼叫一次 —— 即使其引數沒有發生任何變化。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If the pipe has internal state (that is, the result\ndepends on state other than its arguments), set <code>pure</code> to false.\nIn this case, the pipe is invoked on each change-detection cycle,\neven if the arguments have not changed.</p>\n\n\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - api/core/WrappedValue\n - api/core/testing/TestBed\n - api/core/testing/TestBedStatic\n - errors/NG1001\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/migration-injectable\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/testing-pipes\n - guide/testing-utility-apis\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/Pipe#description\n - api/core/Pipe#name\n - api/core/Pipe#options\n - api/core/Pipe#pipe\n - api/core/Pipe#pure\n - api/core/Pipe#see-also\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - guide/glossary#case-types\n - guide/styleguide#02-09\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L817-L825\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L826-L842\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L850-L851\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L817-L825\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L826-L842\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L850-L851\n-->"}